{"tid":2219508,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【手足又輸】平保28元斥3億元「撈底」增持滙豐","createTime":"2020-09-27T02:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T03:42:56.000Z","uid":273218,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"137e90217e3a2198190fd5ef6910a0716ad5d211","tid":2219508,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:32:05.000Z","msg":"【滙豐股價】平保28元斥3億元「撈底」增持滙豐　再超Blackrock成最大股東<br />\n<br />\n滙豐 （00005） 於9月23日（本周三）跌穿28元的世紀供股價，低見27.5元。據聯交所披露，平安資產管理當日在場內斥資3.05億元，以每股均價28.2859元買入1,080萬股滙豐，股權由7.95%升至8%，再次超越貝萊德（Blackrock）成為滙豐大股東。未計今次增持，彭博數據顯示，平保購入滙豐的平均<span class=\"red\">成本價為68.44元</span>。<br />\n<br />\n支國商務部周六發布《不可靠實體清單規定》，然後官媒《環時》首席記者指匯豐很可能成為首批被列入《不可靠實體清單》的外資企業後，匯豐股價隨即急瀉。然而，匯豐未入《不可靠實體清單》，中資股東平保 （02318） 先受傷，3日賬面<span class=\"red\">虧蝕逾30億元</span>。<br />\n<br />\n手足買匯豐日日輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有紀錄以來，匯豐超過40年未試過唔派息<br />\n40年一遇真係唔係好兆頭"},{"pid":"f3e637be9b4c1d2a37f462b7e7357d29c9b4478a","tid":2219508,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vhG3Wsc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvhG3Wsc.jpg&h=2a12f303&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n40年一遇既事都係2020發生"},{"pid":"0cf8fb8aa35606d32ea3eacd627fc6559bc44900","tid":2219508,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:33:45.000Z","msg":"平均價68蚊買左匯豐，好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73386d5c1cd8034a644743827a5780ec37e8430b","tid":2219508,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0cf8fb8aa35606d32ea3eacd627fc6559bc44900","tid":2219508,"ui